<NAME>STRM</NAME>					<VALUE>^\d{1,2}\s*-\s*\d{1,3}\s*-\s*\d+\s*-\s*[W|E]\d$</VALUE>									Section-Township-Range-Meridian, for example: 25-24-1-W5
<NAME>QSTRM</NAME>					<VALUE>^(NE|NW|SE|SW)\s*-\s*\d{1,2}\s*-\s*\d{1,3}\s*-\s*\d+\s*-\s*[W|E]\d$</VALUE>				Quarter Section-Section-Township-Range-Meridian, for example: SW-25-24-1-W5
<NAME>LSTRM</NAME>					<VALUE>^\d+\s*-\s*\d{1,2}\s*-\s*\d{1,3}\s*-\s*\d+\s*-\s*[W|E]\d$</VALUE>						LSD-Section-Township-Range-Meridian, for example: 7-25-24-1-W5
